* ''[[Clossiana kriemhild]]'' <small>(Strecker, 1879)</small>
* [[Перламутровка Матвеева]] ''[[Clossiana matveevi]]'' <small>Gorbunov et Korshunov, 1995</small>
* ''[[Clossiana natazhati]]'' <small>(Gibson, 1920)</small>
* [[Перламутровка оскар]] ''[[Clossiana oscarus]]'' <small>(Eversmann, 1844)</small>
